text: Katrin Dierolf is a German water polo player. She was part of the German women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships and 2007 World Aquatics Championships. She played for the University of Southern California's women's water polo team. == References == == Other websites == * Katrin Dierolf, zimbio * german-katrin-dierolf-r-fights-for-the-ball alamy category:German water polo players Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
